<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2>Course Approved: <%= @course.title %></h2>

      <p>Dear <%= @course.instructor.full_name %>,</p>

      <p>Congratulations! Your course "<%= @course.title %>" has been approved and is now published on the platform.</p>

      <div style="background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <h3>Course Details:</h3>
        <p><strong>Title:</strong> <%= @course.title %></p>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @course.description %></p>
        <p><strong>Approved by:</strong> <%= @approver.email %></p>
        <p><strong>Approval Date:</strong> <%= Time.current.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></p>
      </div>

      <p>Students can now enroll in your course. You will receive notifications for new enrollments and student progress.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>The LMS Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>